ught of the firstlings of his flock and of their fat portions. And the LORD had regard for Abel and for his offering;"}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"Abel also brought of the firstborn of his flock and of their fat. And the LORD respected Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"King James Bible", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock and of the fat thereof. And the LORD had respect unto Abel and to his offering:"}, {:version=>"Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"And Abel also presented an offering--some of the firstborn of his flock and their fat portions. The LORD had regard for Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"Contemporary English Version", :text=>"and Abel also gave an offering to the LORD. He killed the first-born lamb from one of his sheep and gave the LORD the best parts of it. The LORD was pleased with Abel and his offering, "}, {:version=>"Good News Translation", :text=>"Then Abel brought the first lamb born to one of his sheep, killed it, and gave the best parts of it as an offering. The LORD was pleased with Abel and his offering, "}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"And Abel also presented an offering--some of the firstborn of his flock and their fat portions. The LORD had regard for Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"while Abel brought the best parts of some of the firstborn from his flock. The LORD looked favorably upon Abel and his offering, "}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"But Abel brought some of the firstborn of his flock--even the fattest of them. And the LORD was pleased with Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"New Heart English Bible", :text=>"And Abel also brought some of the firstborn of his flock and of its fat. And God looked favorably on Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation", :text=>"Abel also brought some choice parts of the firstborn animals from his flock. The LORD approved of Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"JPS Tanakh 1917", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock and of the fat thereof. And the LORD had respect unto Abel and to his offering;"}, {:version=>"New American Standard 1977 ", :text=>"And Abel, on his part also brought of the firstlings of his flock and of their fat portions. And the LORD had regard for Abel and for his offering;"}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock and of the fat thereof. And the LORD had respect unto Abel and to his offering:"}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstborn of his flock and of the fat thereof. And the LORD had respect to Abel and to his offering:"}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock and of the fat thereof. And Jehovah had respect unto Abel and to his offering:"}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"And Abel also brought of the first born of his sheep and of his fatlings, and God looked upon Abel and his gifts,"}, {:version=>"Douay-Rheims Bible", :text=>"Abel also offered of the firstlings of his flock, and of their fat: and the Lord had respect to Abel, and to his offerings. "}, {:version=>"Darby Bible Translation", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock, and of their fat. And Jehovah looked upon Abel, and on his offering;"}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock and of the fat thereof. And the LORD had respect unto Abel and to his offering:"}, {:version=>"Webster's Bible Translation", :text=>"And Abel, he also brought of the firstlings of his flock, and of the fat thereof. And the LORD had respect to Abel, and to his offering:"}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"Abel also brought some of the firstborn of his flock and of its fat. Yahweh respected Abel and his offering,"}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" and Abel, he hath brought, he also, from the female firstlings of his flock, even from their fat ones; and Jehovah looketh unto Abel and unto his present,"}]}